videos.description: De'Aaron Fox jumps a pass that leads to a fastbreak dunk for Kentucky.
videos.headline: Fox turns defense into offense early

videos.description: Malik Monk slips by his defender with a slick move to set up Isiah Briscoe with an easy layup
videos.headline: Monk shakes defender to set up easy basket

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox lobs a pass up toEdrice "Bam" Adebayo, who throws down a huge dunk.
videos.headline: Bam throws down huge alley-oop jam

videos.description: Mychal Mulder hits a 3-point shot as time expires in the 1st half.
videos.headline: Kentucky takes momentum into half with last second 3-pointer

videos.description: Kentucky head coach John Calipari talks about adjustments the team made to improve as the half went on.
videos.headline: Calipari talks about 1st half adjustments

videos.description: Malik Monk finishes in transition with a huge one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Monk brings the hammer in win

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox finishes a ridiculous layup through a foul.
videos.headline: Fox drops circus shot

videos.description: Dusty Hannahs is called for a flagrant foul after a physical screen.
videos.headline: Arkansas' Hannahs picks up flagrant foul

videos.description: Things get chippy late between Arkansas and Kentucky, culminating with the Razorbacks' Moses Kingsley being ejected after hitting De'Aaron Fox in the face while trying to defend him.
videos.headline: Arkansas' Kingsley ejected after late flagrant foul 2

videos.description: Kentucky head coach John Calipari and senior Dominique Hawkins break down the Wildcats' tournament performance and goals going into the NCAA Tournament.
videos.headline: Calipari and Hawkins talk about Kentucky's team effort

videos.description: Kentucky's De'Aaron Fox, Edrice "Bam" Adebayo and Dominique Hawkins are name to the SEC all-tournament team.
videos.headline: Fox, Adebayo and Hawkins named to all-tournament team

videos.description: Malik Monk scores 17 points as No. 8 Kentucky improves to 29-5 with an 82-65 victory over Arkansas.
videos.headline: Kentucky tops Arkansas to win SEC title
